videos.headline: Louisville strikes early with 52-yd TD
videos.description: Trey Smith finds an opening and runs 52 yards into the end zone on Louisville's first drive of the game.

videos.headline: Wake Forest answers with 28-yd TD pass
videos.description: Sam Hartman finds Jack Freudenthal for a 28-yard Wake Forest touchdown.

videos.headline: Colburn finds a hole for a 56-yard Wake Forest TD
videos.description: Matt Colburn continues to shine for the Demon Deacons with his second rushing touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Wake Forest scoop-and score-play increases lead
videos.description: Wake Forest's Carlos Basham Jr. recovers a fumble and runs into the end zone to give the Demon Deacons a 35-14 lead over Louisville.

videos.headline: Colburn finds another opening with 12-yd TD run
videos.description: Matt Colburn strikes again with a 12-yard touchdown run for Wake Forest.
